                            <li>內容重點：...（以下省略）</li>
                            <li>相關背景資料：...（以下省略）</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div></div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="collapsible-container border-b border-gray-200 py-4">
                    <button class="collapsible-trigger w-full text-left flex justify-between items-center">
                        <h3 class="subtitle font-semibold text-teal-700">範例2：從官網新聞稿參考同議題背景資料，擬定新的新聞稿</h3>
                         <span class="plus-minus-icon text-2xl font-light text-teal-700">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="collapsible-content"><div class="pt-4 prompt-block">
                        <button class="copy-btn" title="複製提示詞">複製</button>
